Reasoning: The paper is about robotics and specifically addresses the problem of incompatibility between robot components. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.RO (Robotics). The paper also proposes a model for creating plug-and-play robot hardware components, which involves artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and systems engineering (cs.SY). Additionally, the paper emphasizes the need for interoperability and comparability of robotics technology, which relates to software engineering (cs.SE) and human-computer interaction (cs.HC).
